high_descs: turn right, then walk along the counter top to your right until you reach the opposite end
pick up the knife in front of the apple on the counter top
turn around and face the wooden table behind you
slice the potato on the wooden table
turn around and face the microwave on the counter top
place the knife on the plate which is on the counter top
return to facing the wooden kitchen table
pick up a slice of potato from the table
face the refrigerator to the left of the table
open the door and place the potato slice in front of the black mug on the shelf, then shut the door for a few seconds and open the door and grab the potato slice
go back to the microwave on the counter top
place the potato on the counter top to the right of the plate and knife
anns.task_desc: slice the potato and cool it down in the refrigerator so it can be returned to the counter top

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the microwave at the end of the bench.
Pick up the knife on the bench.
Turn around and take the knife to the dining table.
Cut the potato into slices.
Turn around and walk back to the microwave with the knife.
Place the knife on the plate to the right of the microwave.
Turn around and walk back to the dining table.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the potato slice on the top shelf, and then close the door, wait eight seconds before opening the door and removing the potato slice.
Turn around and walk back to the plate next to the microwave.
Place the potato slice on the bench to the right of the plate.
anns.task_desc: Place a refrigerated slice of potato on the bench.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk across the kitchen, then turn to the counter top on your right.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the counter top.
Turn around and go to the table across from you.
Cut the potato between the fork and the head of lettuce, on the table, into slices.
Turn around and go to the counter top to the right of the microwave across from you.
Place the knife on the plate, that is on the counter top.
Turn around and go back to the table across from you.
Pick up one of the potato slices previously cut.
Turn to your left and go to the refrigerator on your right.
Place the potato slice in front of the coffee cup, on the top shelf of the refrigerator, wait a moment for the potato slice to chill, then remove the potato slice from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go back to the counter top to the right of the microwave.
Place the potato slice on the counter, to the right of the plate and knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato slice on the counter, and a knife on a plate on the same counter.
